author: senh
title: Annaleigh Ashford channels her inner canine for 'Sylvia'
text:
Associated Press , Monday - 10/19/2015 - 06:34 PM 
An aging gangster went on trial Monday on charges he was in on the $6 million Lufthansa holdup in 1978, a legendary theft dramatized in the hit film "Goodfellas." ‘Good Wife’ Star to Play Johnny Carson in Showtime’s ‘I’m Dying Up Here’ Comedy Pilot Variety , Monday - 10/19/2015 - 06:21 PM 
Showtime’s comedy “I’m Dying Up Here” has added a slew of guest stars to the cast of the one-hour pilot. “The Good Wife’s” recurring player Dylan Baker has been cast as Johnny Carson. Baker’s work on the CBS legal drama, playing Colin Sweeney, earned him three Emmy nominations for outstanding guest actor in a drama series
